:::The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare/Hun-Grr:::

Skywarp: That was easy.
Dirge: Almost too easy...
Ramjet: Dont worry about it, they seem nice enough. Destrons!  We have been 
invited into their base. Lets go in now and wait to see their leader.
::My Destrons fly to entrance, waiting for the entrance to open::
~~~~~
::Hun-Grr returns to see Motormaster and Megatron fighting::
Hun-Grr: YES! we fight!
::Cyclonus and Scourge immeadiatley point their guns at Hun-grr and 
Sinnertwin::
Scourge: Foolish Terrorcons! This is a battle over leadership.
Cyclonus: Any one who intereferes will likely get killed in the crossfire.
::Hun-Grr reluctantly dropped his weapon and backed off, but Cyclonus and 
Scourge still had their guns on Sinnertwin::

--part1_40.91b71bd.27ea78af_boundary
